7
00:00:35,400 --> 00:00:38,766
- My account’s private.
- Sis!

8
00:00:38,766 --> 00:00:42,233
I’m really happy to be in Kitakyushu with you.

9
00:00:42,466 --> 00:00:45,500
I like Kitakyushu too.

10
00:00:45,766 --> 00:00:48,033
Especially when you’re here with me.

11
00:01:29,933 --> 00:01:31,733
You’re not setting private anymore?

12
00:01:34,900 --> 00:01:36,566
Nope, not anymore.

13
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,700
What make you change your mind?

14
00:01:42,833 --> 00:01:45,700
You wouldn’t even let me follow you before.

15
00:01:46,100 --> 00:01:48,700
Well, now you can. Isn’t that good?

16
00:01:51,866 --> 00:01:52,966
It’s good.

17
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:54,566
I love it.

18
00:02:07,066 --> 00:02:08,066
Pick up, sis.

19
00:02:17,500 --> 00:02:19,333
Hello, Khun Mind.

20
00:02:19,366 --> 00:02:23,933
May I ask what business you have WITH MY P’Aokbab?

21
00:02:37,066 --> 00:02:40,300
Babe, tell her we’re on our honeymoon.

22
00:02:45,700 --> 00:02:48,866
If there’s nothing else, we’ll hang up now.

23
00:02:48,900 --> 00:02:51,500
We’ve got more romantic time to spend.

24
00:02:51,900 --> 00:02:55,033
Sayonara, Khun Mind-san!

25
00:02:55,033 --> 00:02:58,033
Bleh!

26
00:03:00,166 --> 00:03:01,666
What on earth are you doing?

27
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:04,766
Talking to Mind-san, what else?

28
00:03:04,966 --> 00:03:05,900
Ugh.

29
00:03:10,033 --> 00:03:11,800
Ugh, it’s so cold, sis.

30
00:03:11,900 --> 00:03:13,266
Let me hug you.

31
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:16,233
My hands are freezing.

32
00:03:16,500 --> 00:03:18,100
Hey, let go!

33
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:19,400
But it’s cold!

34
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,266
Come on, just a little.

35
00:03:29,266 --> 00:03:32,566
Fine, fine—come here, it’s cold anyway.

36
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:01,366
Yahh—

37
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:02,200
You okay?

38
00:04:02,300 --> 00:04:03,400
I’m not drunk.

39
00:04:03,666 --> 00:04:05,066
See? I still walk straight.

40
00:04:15,566 --> 00:04:17,633
Such a romantic night, isn’t it?

41
00:04:17,933 --> 00:04:19,233
Yeah.

42
00:04:22,566 --> 00:04:23,966
Do you think—

43
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:26,066
we should kiss again?

44
00:04:26,266 --> 00:04:27,266
What—hey!

45
00:04:28,033 --> 00:04:30,300
Khun Ming wouldn’t do that.

46
00:04:32,066 --> 00:04:34,733
We’re walking on the street, have some shame.

47
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:38,633
Why be shy? The more people see, the better.

48
00:04:38,633 --> 00:04:41,333
Let everyone see how much we love each other.

49
00:04:43,700 --> 00:04:45,533
Stop right there, you little puppy.

50
00:04:45,700 --> 00:04:49,100
I’m not a puppy, I’m a little kitty—meow.

51
00:04:50,166 --> 00:04:51,700
Haven’t you had enough?

52
00:04:51,966 --> 00:04:53,400
Think of it as payment.

53
00:04:53,433 --> 00:04:55,966
For saving you from that old hag earlier.

54
00:04:55,966 --> 00:04:57,666
You call that saving me?

55
00:04:58,500 --> 00:05:01,100
I knew you didn’t want to talk to her.

56
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:02,300
Yeah?

57
00:05:02,300 --> 00:05:04,166
Still, don’t you think that was too much?

58
00:05:04,900 --> 00:05:06,166
I was just doing my duty.

59
00:05:06,366 --> 00:05:07,333
What duty?

60
00:05:07,766 --> 00:05:09,766
Protecting the one I love.

61
00:05:11,466 --> 00:05:13,966
You’re really in character, Khun Ming.

62
00:05:24,500 --> 00:05:26,700
I’m serious though.

63
00:05:26,733 --> 00:05:28,533
I’m actually flirting with you.

64
00:05:34,700 --> 00:05:35,566
Hm?

65
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,366
